description: I love shopping-center. They are one of the best places to find some younger guys who regularly love to hang around. But today the center was quite empty. So I entered the supermarket and finally I found some nice boy. He wanted to cook something special for his girlfriend and was looking for good oil. Well, I told him that I make some market-research and involved him into a small interview. I also asked him about his opinion about the "Fast Money" shows. He was quite open and I invited him on a coffee where I offered him damn good money to show me his body. Well, what can I say? We ended in the cabin of the center-toilet. And he had much more to offer than just his chest.
title: Czech Hunter 24
